Exhibition Fair and Publicity.details:
The scheme “Exhibition Fair and Publicity” launched by the Horticulture and Food Processing Department, Government of Madhya Pradesh aims to spread awareness about horticultural technologies and departmental schemes through exhibitions and seminars conducted at district and block levels for the benefit of farmers.
&lt;br&gt;

